title: 1926 Chicago Cardinals season
text: The <a href="1926%20NFL%20season">1926</a> <a href="Chicago%20Cardinals">Chicago Cardinals</a> season was their seventh in the <a href="National%20Football%20League">National Football League</a>. The team failed to improve on their <a href="1925%20Chicago%20Cardinals%20season">previous output</a> of 11–2–1, winning only five games. They finished tenth in the league.
